---
import Header from '../components/header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
const pageTitle = "ronxvier";
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
	<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
	  <div>
      <h1 class="mainhead">Ronel Xavier</h1>
	    <h2 class="subhead">[ronxvier]</h2>
	  </div>
	  <img
	    src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/188875524?v=4"
	    alt="GitHub profile picture"
	    style="width: 90px; height: 90px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;"
	  />
	</div>
  <div >
    <p class="quote">"Volume negates luck."</p>
    <p>This site exists primarily to document the <a href="../projects">[projects]</a> I've completed as I add more throughout uni. I've also added a <a href="../blog">[blog]</a> section, which I may use to keep record of my notes, given the blog entries use the same markdown format as <a href="https://obsidian.md" target = "_blank">[obsidian.md]</a>. I'll also be using it to loosely document what Iâ€™m exploring over time.</p>
  </div>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>



<style>
  p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
	a:link {
	  color: #D8B4D6;
	  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
	  font-weight: 100;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: text-shadow 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
	}

	a:visited {
	  color: #CBBACD;
	  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
	  font-weight: 300;
	  text-decoration: none;
	}

	a:hover,
	a:focus {
	  color: #D8B4D6;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(130, 90, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .mainhead {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-optical-sizing: auto;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .subhead{
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-optical-sizing: auto;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 0; 
      color: #8a9fbf;
      transition: text-shadow 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .quote{
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-optical-sizing: auto;
      font-weight: 450;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 1rem; 
      margin-bottom: 0rem; 
      color: #A2A8D3;
  }
  .subhead:hover {
    color: #a5b8e8;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(112, 66, 255, 1);
  }

</style>
